{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_05_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 お姉さんになりたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さとみによるパジャマユニット結成前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Before Satomi formed the pajama unit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "んしょ……資料は、このくらいでいい、かな……\n後は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm… This much should be enough for the documents‚ I guess…\nAfterwards…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1000000159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "忙しそうだな、雫\n確か、寮で合宿するって聞いたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem busy‚ Shizuku.\nI heard you're going to have a training camp at the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3666666825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.6666666825
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、さとみさんが、新ユニットの企画で悩んでるから\nみんなで合宿して、もっとアイデアを出す……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ Satomi-san is struggling with plans for the new unit‚\nso we're going to brainstorm together during the camp…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8000000159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんと私は、合宿に必要な物を準備する係……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan and I are in charge of preparing stuffs for the camp…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8666684628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.833334748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、すずちゃん、すみれちゃんは\n引率のさとみさんと、買い出しに行ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro-chan‚ Suzu-chan‚ and Sumire-chan are\nout shopping with Satomi-san who's supervising them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.533334748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "引率って……学校の先生じゃないんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Supervising… Isn't she a teacher at school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5000003974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.5000003974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "おやつは、三百円まで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Snacks should cost up to $3…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5000003974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遠足でもないんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this isn't a school field trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1666660468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、冗談……\n私は、事務所の資料を、寮に運ぶつもり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ just kidding…\nI plan to take office materials to the dorm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666660468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル雑誌とかだよな\n会社の物も、自由に持って行っていいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like idol magazines‚ right?\nYou're free to take company items as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4666660468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4333322048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……雑誌ならみんなで読めるし\nきっと参考になるはず。解説も、任せて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you… If it's magazines‚ we can all read them together‚\nand it should be helpful. I'll handle the explanations…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8209105968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "後は、瑠依さんと組ませてもらった時の経験も\n参考になりそうだし……話せたらいいなって思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ the experience I had when I was paired with Rui-san\nseems like it could be useful too… I hope I can talk about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5333367825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.1333357652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "――ううん、思うだけじゃなくて\nちゃんと伝えられたら、いいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not just thinking about it‚ but\nit'd be great if I could convey it properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333357652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.300000906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで意見を出し合うの、いい刺激になるし\nさとみさんのためにも、精一杯頑張る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sharing opinions with everyone is a great stimulus‚ and\nI'll do my best for Satomi-san's sake…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1666675727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "雫がついていれば、橋本さんも心強いだろうな\nやる気も十分……というか、だいぶ燃えてないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having you around must be reassuring for Hashimoto-san too.\nYou seem pretty motivated… or rather‚ fired up‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.3666665554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "燃えて当たり前……\nこの展開は、美味し過ぎるので……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being fired up is natural…\nThis development is just too delicious…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5999998887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "美味しい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Delicious…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8999998887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.4666650295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "自分の考える、最高のユニットを作る……\nドルオタなら、誰もが夢見る美味しい展開……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Creating the best unit according to my own ideas…\nIt's a delicious development that any idol fan would dream of…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7999983628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.833334748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんも、同じ道を歩む者……\nドルオタ同士、語り合いたいと思ってた……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-san‚ who walks the same path…\nI've always wanted to talk with fellow idol fans…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.133334748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "それに……同年代の子達と\n好きなものを語り合えるのも……いいなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also… being able to talk about our favorite things with\npeople of the same age…It's nice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5000105699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.7000176907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "学校だと、あんまりそういう話、したことなくて\n一緒に語れるだけで、幸せ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike school‚ where I haven't had many such conversations‚\njust being able to talk together makes me happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2000176907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、確かに好きなものを語り合うって\nそれだけで楽しいよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ talking about your favorite things with others…\nThat alone is enjoyable‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8000166734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.9333418687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "うん、凄く楽しい……！\n合宿でもいっぱい語り合って、いっぱい力になる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's really enjoyable…!\nI'm looking forward to lots of conversations and getting stronger during the camp…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.8000085354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺も橋本さんの企画書、楽しみにしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to Hashimoto-san's proposal too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.5666701158,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6699.996550899982,
          "startTime": 164.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5999.996948199992,
          "startTime": 163.566667064
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日、ユニット結成後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later after unit formation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.7333367825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4000003974
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4000003974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "雫、お疲れ様。橋本さんの企画書を見たよ\nまさか合宿のメンバーでユニットを組むなんてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ good job. I've seen Hashimoto's proposal.\nIt's surprising that you're forming a unit with the members from the camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.6333408516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "うん、自分でも、びっくり……\nまさか、選んでもらえるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ even I'm surprised.\nI didn't expect to be chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.1666731676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.2000136217
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットのコンセプトは\n『プロのアイドルではなく、素の魅力を強調』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concept of the unit is emphasizing the natural charm\nrather than professional idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.6333469551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.2333235582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "これは、アリ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's acceptable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.2333235582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "雫のお墨付きって訳だな。センターはすみれだったが\nどうやって決めたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like Shizuku approved it‚\neven though Sumire was the center‚ how did you decide?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.6999881904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.4999881904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんの英断……コンセプトを一番\n体現していたのは、すみれちゃんだったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was Satomi-san's bold decision…\nSumire-chan was the one who best embodied the concept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1999881904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "みんな納得のセンター……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone agreed on her as the center…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.0666558743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.5999881904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すずちゃんは、少しだけ悔しかったのかも……\nでもいろいろ考えて……すみれちゃんを認めた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Suzu-chan might have been a little disappointed…\nBut after considering various things… she acknowledged Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.166654857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.2999942939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "そこには、確かな友情が芽生えていた……\nアイドル達はぶつかり合って、成長する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a definite friendship budding there…\nIdols clash and grow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.1333276272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "後半、なんだかナレーション風だったが\nなんにせよ、楽しい雰囲気だったんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The latter part sounded like a narration‚\nbut it was still fun‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.3999942939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 231.6333276272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk024.m4a",
      "text": "うん、楽しかった……\n枕投げしたり、凄く盛り上がった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was fun…\nWe did pillow fight and got really excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.6666609605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "合宿の目的、忘れそうだったくらい、かも……\n私も、一緒になって脱線しちゃって……反省",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so lively that we almost forgot the purpose of the camp…\nI also got carried away… I need to reflect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.0666917166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 248.7333316962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk026.m4a",
      "text": "私より、年下の子が多いし……\nここから千紗ちゃんと一緒に支えていきたい、な……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many younger kids than me…\nI want to support members with Chisa-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.6666650295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 257.766679271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "雫は、年下の子と組むの初めてだったか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was this your first time working with younger kids?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.766679271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk027.m4a",
      "text": "うん、今回は、私がお姉ちゃん……\nサニピで言うと、遙子さんポジション……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ this time‚ I'm the big sister…\nIn terms of Sunny Peace‚ I'm in the position of Haruko-san…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.9333459377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 269.3333601792
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk028.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私がついてるから、大丈夫よ……\nみたいな感じで、いきたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ it'll be okay because I'm with you…\nI want to go with that feeling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.6333601792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 276.0000024318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そういう雰囲気が似合うかはともかく……\n初めてのことだし、いい経験になるといいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether that vibe suits you or not…\nIt's your first time‚ so I hope it's a good experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.2000024318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 282.7333357651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk029.m4a",
      "text": "うん、すみれちゃんも、初めてセンターをやる\nみたいだし、支えてあげられたら、いいなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ Sumire-chan is also doing the center for the first time…\nI hope I can support her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.7666690985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 291.6333439032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_01-szk030.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、練習行ってきます……\nまた、ね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I'll go to practice…\nSee you later…",
        "id": ""
      },
